=head1 DESCRIPTION

The parameters for a control. A control can have zero, one, or more
than one parameter. An example of a control with two parameters is:
"backup plan frequency is at least C<daily> and the retention period is
at least C<1 year>". The first parameter is C<daily>. The second
parameter is C<1 year>.

